        "text": "7. THE MINISTERIAL ATTIRE OF THE PRIESTS.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(40) For Aaron’s sons thou shalt make coats—i.e., linen tunics like that of the high priest already described (see the last Note on Exodus 28:39), but not woven in any peculiar fashion.",
